      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PADOVA (6) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 1.5 lengths at this track in a handy 19.63. Awkwardly drawn but has a good record over this journey. The form out of his last race has been franked. Expected to measure up again. CASINO SPECIAL (5) was in the placings last time but prior to that he ran a superb 19.60 win over 366m at this track. Should be in this for a long way. RINSED THE LOT (1) is a fast dog well performed over the sprint races. Was fourth last time (20.10) over 366m at this track in a Free For All. Form at the trip excellent including six wins. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Likely to be thereabouts. RECONSTRUCTION (2) warrants respect with the drop in journey.",
